OL,9,FA people smuggler in Quetta, who       
OL,10,Farranges illegal routes out of         
OL,11,FPakistan, is explaining his business   
OL,12,Fmodel to an undercover BBC journalist. 
OL,13,FFor 2.5m Pakistani rupees ($9000;      
OL,14,F#7,500), a young man can arrive in     
OL,15,FEurope "safe and sound" in             
OL,16,Fapproximately three weeks, he says, by 
OL,17,Fcrossing the border into Iran on foot  
OL,18,Fand then travelling by road via Turkey 
OL,19,Fto Italy. His tone is reassuring.      
